<span class="PRTitle"><!-- NewsTitle.start -->SEN. GRACE POE PRESS CONFERENCE TRANSCRIPT<!-- NewsTitle.end --></span>
<br /><span class="PRSub"><!-- NewsTitleSub.start -->KORONADAL CITY<!-- NewsTitleSub.end--></span>
